"{\"uid\": \"pakobserver.net-badminton-star-an-fires-olympic-warning-with-paris-title\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Badminton world number one An Se-young fired an Olympic warning after winning the French Open title in the Paris arena that will stage matches this summer.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996970221222, \"rank\": 3.0297795137827026e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The South Korean won her 21st BWF World Tour crown and second of the year with an 18-21, 21-13, 21-10 defeat of Japanese rival Akane Yamaguchi on Sunday in the French capital.\", \"from\": 157, \"to\": 332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 161, \"end\": 177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korean_won\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"South Korean won\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korean_won\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korean_won\"}, {\"begin\": 187, \"end\": 201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BWF_World_Tour\", \"score\": 0.9999246834685804, \"rank\": 7.528255709683275e-05, \"text\": \"BWF World Tour\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BWF_World_Tour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BWF_World_Tour\"}, {\"begin\": 269, \"end\": 277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.898622246045046, \"rank\": 0.10557152287844031, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 284, \"end\": 299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akane_Yamaguchi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Akane Yamaguchi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akane_Yamaguchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akane_Yamaguchi\"}, {\"begin\": 317, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8406073050242744, \"rank\": 0.1576240631707341, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old An, who will be favourite to win a first Olympic gold in four months' time, said: \\\"This is an important event before the Olympics and I felt a lot of pressure at first.\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Winning in the Olympic arena means a lot and I feel very happy.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I guess when I come back here for the Olympics I will be in a positive frame of mind.\\\"\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 672, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The tournament at Porte de la Chapelle Arena was also treated as a test event for Paris Olympic organisers.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 692, \"end\": 712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porte_de_la_Chapelle_(Paris_M\\u00e9tro)\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Porte de la Chapelle\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porte_de_la_Chapelle_(Paris_M\\u00e9tro)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porte_de_la_Chapelle_(Paris_M\\u00e9tro)\"}, {\"begin\": 756, \"end\": 761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996970221222, \"rank\": 3.0297795137827026e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An has risen to the top of women's badminton after a breakthrough 2023, but she has struggled in recent weeks with a knee injury.\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Former world number one Yamaguchi, who has also been held back by recent injury, was contesting her first World Tour final since September.\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 1053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 938, \"end\": 947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akane_Yamaguchi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9361875424318987e-22, \"text\": \"Yamaguchi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akane_Yamaguchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akane_Yamaguchi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 26-year-old said that she ran out of steam in the 64-minute title decider.\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I slowed down in the third,\\\" said the Japanese player, ranked four in the world.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1173, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.898622246045046, \"rank\": 0.10557152287844031, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Right now my condition is much better (than two months ago) and I was able to make the final, but I feel there is some more way to go.\\\"\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1353, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China's Shi Yuqi, number two in the world, won the men's French Open title with a 22-20, 21-19 victory over Thailand's Kunlavut Vitidsarn.\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1355, \"end\": 1360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9387978187998611, \"rank\": 0.03490026447164938, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1363, \"end\": 1371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shi_Yuqi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shi Yuqi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shi_Yuqi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shi_Yuqi\"}, {\"begin\": 1463, \"end\": 1471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_badminton_team\", \"score\": 0.9999862745024248, \"rank\": 1.36103471647798e-05, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_badminton_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_badminton_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1474, \"end\": 1492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kunlavut_Vitidsarn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kunlavut Vitidsarn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kunlavut_Vitidsarn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kunlavut_Vitidsarn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The All England Open, one of the most prestigious tournaments in badminton, begins on Tuesday.-AFP    \\u00a9All rights reserved | Pakistan Observer\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1636, \"entities\": []}]}"